Carolina Milena Jaume Saporiti (amụrụ ya na 18 Ọktoba 1976) bụ onye obodo Ecuadorian na-eme ihe nkiri na onye na-eme ihe ngosi.

yaA mụrụ Carolina Jaume na 18 Ọktoba 1985 na obodo kachasị ukwuu nke Ecuador, Guayaquil, nne na nna ya bụ Rafael Jaume nke Puerto Rico na Diana Saporiti, onye bụbu onye na-emepụta ihe onyonyo si Ecuador
Jaume malitere n'oge na-eme ihe nkiri na TV, mana ọ hapụrụ n'oge ọ na-eto eto ruo mgbe ọ dị afọ iri na itoolu, mgbe ọ banyere n'asọmpi Queen of Guayaquil nke afọ 2004, a kpọrọ ya "Star of October"

Jaume mere ihe nkiri mbụ ya na TV n'afọ 2006 na telenovela Amores que matan [es] nke Ecuavisa mepụtara na usoro De 9 a 6, ebe ya na Xavier Pimentel [es], di ya n'ọdịnihu rụkọrọ ọrụ. N'afọ 2007, Jaume ga-amụ nwa nwanyị di na nwunye ahụ, mana alụmdi na nwunye ahụ kwụsịrị otu afọ mgbe e mesịrị, n'afọ 2009.

N'afọ 2008, Jaume pụtara na Ihe nkiri telenovela El Secreto de Toño Palomino [es] na afọ sochirinụ sonyere na ihe nkiri La Panadería na telenovela El exitoso Lcdo Cardoso [es], mana ọ hapụrụ ha abụọ tupu emechaa mgbe ọ gbara arụkwaghịm na Ecuavisa

N'ikpeazụ, ọ ga-ahụ onwe ya na Channel One na-arụ ọrụ dị ka onye ngosi, mana ọ ga-ahapụkwa Channel One n'afọ 2015 wee lụọ onye ọchụnta ego Ecuadorian Allan Zenck ma mụọ nwa ọzọ. Site n'ebe ahụ, Jaume ga-enye aka na nhazi nke Mujer que se respeta na Claudia Camposano na Marcela Ruete.
N'afọ 2016, Jaume laghachiri Ecuavisa ka ọ bụrụ onye ọka ikpe na oge nke ise nke Ecuador's Got Talent [es]
Otú ọ dị, n'ihi echiche dị iche na onye ọka ikpe ibe ya bụ Paola Farias, nkwekọrịta ya amaliteghị ma ọ hapụrụ ụlọ ọrụ ahụ nke ugboro abụọ.
